'''南非簽證政策'''是南非政府決定誰人可進入[[南非|南非]]的政策。前往南非的遊客必須從南非的其中一個駐外機構獲得[[簽證|簽證]]，並需要出示該國簽證才能入境，除非他們是來自免簽證國家，在這種情況下，他們會獲得所謂的“入境口岸簽證”。簽證需要親自申請，且提供[[生物特徵識別|生物特徵識別]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/politics/new-visa-rules-will-hurt-tourism-da-1.1707884#.U6hYw7HLNEM|title=New visa rules will hurt tourism: DA – IOL News|publisher=|accessdate=8 March 2018|archive-date=2015-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150419102309/http://www.iol.co.za/news/politics/new-visa-rules-will-hurt-tourism-da-1.1707884#.U6hYw7HLNEM|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

根據規定，来访者的护照有效期不得少于1个月，且剩餘空白頁不得少於1頁（如果需要簽證則為2頁）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.home-affairs.gov.za/index.php/countries-exempt-from-sa-visas |title=Department of Home Affairs – Exempt Countries |website=www.home-affairs.gov.za |accessdate=8 March 2018 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180118122654/http://www.home-affairs.gov.za/index.php/countries-exempt-from-sa-visas |archive-date=2018-01-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2016年12月，南非宣布將根據互惠原則審查其簽證政策<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thesouthafrican.com/dha-revokes-visa-free-travel-for-new-zealand-nationals-but-thats-just-the-beginning/ |title=DHA revokes visa free travel for New Zealand nationals, but that’s just the beginning |first=Ezra |last=Claymore |date=14 December 2016 |publisher= |accessdate=8 March 2018 |archive-date=2019-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421070943/https://www.thesouthafrican.com/dha-revokes-visa-free-travel-for-new-zealand-nationals-but-thats-just-the-beginning/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2018年3月，南非宣布將在2019年3月31日之前試行電子簽證系統第一階段<ref>{{cite web |url=https://businesstech.co.za/news/mobile/233185/electronic-visas-to-be-piloted-in-south-africa/ |title=Electronic visas to be piloted in South Africa |date=22 March 2018 |accessdate=2019-04-21 |archive-date=2019-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190421070941/https://businesstech.co.za/news/mobile/233185/electronic-visas-to-be-piloted-in-south-africa/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2018年9月，南非宣布阿爾及利亞、埃及、摩洛哥、加納、阿拉伯聯合酋長國、卡塔爾、伊朗、黎巴嫩、巴勒斯坦國、白俄羅斯、格魯吉亞以及古巴的公民將能夠免簽證訪問南非<ref name="#1">{{cite web |url=http://www.dha.gov.za/index.php/statements-speeches/1186-statement-by-the-minister-of-home-affairs-mr-malusi-gigaba-mp-at-the-media-briefing-on-visa-related-reforms-in-pretoria-on-25-september-2018?platform=hootsuite |title=Department of Home Affairs – Speeches Statements – The Minister of Home Affairs Mr Malusi Gigaba Mp at the Media Briefing on Visa Related Reforms in Pretoria on 25 September 2018 |access-date=2019-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180927125336/http://www.dha.gov.za/index.php/statements-speeches/1186-statement-by-the-minister-of-home-affairs-mr-malusi-gigaba-mp-at-the-media-briefing-on-visa-related-reforms-in-pretoria-on-25-september-2018?platform=hootsuite |archive-date=2018-09-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。電子簽證試點計劃將在2019年4月於紐西蘭開始<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.southafricavisa.com/e-visa-south-africa-launch/ |title=South African new e-visa will be piloted in New Zealand by 31 March 2019 |website=www.southafricavisa.com |accessdate=20 March 2019 |archive-date=2019-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329101410/https://www.southafricavisa.com/e-visa-south-africa-launch/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，在完成簽證豁免協議後，聖多美和普林西比、阿拉伯撒哈拉民主共和國、突尼斯、巴林、阿曼、科威特以及沙特阿拉伯的國民也將能夠在短期逗留期間免簽證旅行到南非<ref name="#1"/>。

