== 超期停留后果 ==
根据2002年修订的《南非移民法》第13条，超出南非签证滞留期限的外国国民将被确定为“不受欢迎的”人士，将面临被禁止入境长达5年的处罚<ref>{{cite web|title=Overstay Visa South Africa|url=http://www.savisas.com/visa-overstay-appeals/|accessdate=7 October 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151110050738/http://www.savisas.com/visa-overstay-appeals|archive-date=2015-11-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

== 未成年人 ==
从2015年6月1日起，所有18岁以下进出南非的未成年人必须持有护照、父母双方详细资料以及未经删节的[[出生证明书|出生证明书]]<ref>{{Cite web|title = Travelling with children to or from South Africa? Child Visa Checklist app helps|url = http://www.drivesouthafrica.co.za/child-visa-checklist/|website = Drive South Africa|accessdate = 2015-10-15|archive-date = 2016-10-27|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161027174025/https://www.drivesouthafrica.co.za/child-visa-checklist/|dead-url = yes}}</ref>。该要求适用于国内和国外公民。如果孩子只与父母一方旅行，则需要另一方提供的同意书。如果孩子与另一位成年人一起旅行且没有父母双方，则必须出示父母双方的同意书。无人陪伴的未成年人除了持有同意书和出生证明外，还必须提供当地南非接待方的必要信息<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.travelstart.co.za/lp/travel-tips/unabridged-birth-certificate-for-minors|title=Unabridged Birth Certificates – Travelstart.co.za|website=www.travelstart.co.za|accessdate=8 March 2018|archive-date=2019-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190423120726/https://www.travelstart.co.za/lp/travel-tips/unabridged-birth-certificate-for-minors|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.enca.com/opinion/how-travel-children-and-out-sa|title=How to travel with children into and out of SA|website=www.enca.com|accessdate=8 March 2018|archive-date=2019-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422102132/https://www.enca.com/opinion/how-travel-children-and-out-sa|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该规则受到旅游业的广泛批评，但官员声称该规则的实施是为了打击南非普遍的[[人口贩卖|人口贩卖]]和单方面儿童监护权滥用的情况<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.biznews.com/grubstreet/front-pages/2015/05/22/the-sorry-messy-unabridged-birth-certificate-saga-sa-front-pages-fri2015-05-22/|title=The sorry, messy unabridged birth certificate saga: SA front pages, 2015-05-22|publisher=|accessdate=8 March 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150530094345/http://www.biznews.com/grubstreet/front-pages/2015/05/22/the-sorry-messy-unabridged-birth-certificate-saga-sa-front-pages-fri2015-05-22/|archive-date=2015-05-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/news/South-Africas-new-rules-on-travelling-with-children-may-deter-families/|title=South Africa's new rules on travelling with children 'may deter families'|first=Chris|last=Leadbeater|date=4 February 2016|publisher=|accessdate=8 March 2018|via=www.telegraph.co.uk|archive-date=2019-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422102123/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/travel/news/South-Africas-new-rules-on-travelling-with-children-may-deter-families/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2016年10月，由于完整的出生证明要求，已有13,000多名游客无法进入该国，从而对经济产生了负面影响<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.iol.co.za/travel/travel-news/new-visa-rules-13-000-denied-entry-into-sa-2085274|title=New visa rules: 13 000 denied entry into SA {{!}} IOL|access-date=2016-11-04|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104113613/http://www.iol.co.za/travel/travel-news/new-visa-rules-13-000-denied-entry-into-sa-2085274|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2018年9月，内阁宣布他们打算取消这项有争议的儿童旅行要求<ref>{{cite news |url=https://businesstech.co.za/news/government/272907/more-details-on-south-africas-new-visa-rules-revealed/ |title=More details on South Africa’s new visa rules revealed |publisher=BusinessTech |date=2018-09-20 |accessdate=2019-11-18 |archive-date=2019-07-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190722203108/https://businesstech.co.za/news/government/272907/more-details-on-south-africas-new-visa-rules-revealed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

